ccokdezahescbgdggctiyozaageeicemjsfeiati length 6 146073 page 146073 <!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/><meta name="twitter:site" content="@verge"/><meta property="fb:app_id" content="549923288395304"/><meta property="og:site_name" content="The Verge"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"/><meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Verge"/><meta name="google-site-verification" content="IucFf_TKtbFFH8_YeFyEteQIwYPdANM1R46_U9DpAr4"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="The Verge" href="/rss/index.xml"/><title>Twitter is funding research into a decentralized version of its platform - The Verge</title><meta name="robots" content="index,follow,max-image-preview:large"/><meta name="description" content="Twitter CEO Jack Dorsey has announced that the company is funding research into a decentralized social networking protocol under the name Bluesky, offering a solution to moderation problems and other issues."/><meta property="og:title" content="Twitter is funding research into a decentralized version of its platform"/><meta property="og:description" content="CEO Jack Dorsey says Twitter could adopt the system"/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.theverge.com/2019/12/11/21010856/twitter-jack-dorsey-bluesky-decentralized-social-network-research-moderation"/><meta property="og:type" content="article"/><meta property="article:published_time" content="2019-12-11T15:09:49.000Z"/><meta property="article:modified_time" content="2019-12-11T15:09:49.000Z"/><meta property="og:image" content="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XZnbR9ootgvPweoYsQIOwxJo15Q=/0x0:2040x1360/1200x628/filters:focal(1020x680:1021x681)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/11596527/akrales_180620_1777_0303.jpg"/><meta property="og:image:type" content="image/jpeg"/><meta property="og:image:width" content="1200"/><meta property="og:image:height" co